      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "ORGANIZED labor won a victory\nin the superior court this morning\nwhen Judge Hinkle threw out the\ninjunction proceedings brought by\ncertain restaurant Keepers against\nthe allied crafts to restrain picket\ning places called unfair\n\n\nA temporary injunction had been\ngranted and on hearing to make 1t\npermanent Judge Hinkle ruled that\nthere was no evidence to justify\nan injunction against the alliance\nor any of the unions. 2. O. Con-\nnor appeared for the unions and\nSam Edelstein for the restaurant\nkeepers involved."
    }
